<abstract><t>In-situ Flow Information Telemetry (iFIT) is a framework for applying data plane telemetry techniques such as In-situ OAM (iOAM) and Postcard-Based Telemetry (PBT).  It enumerates several key components and describes how these components are assembled to achieve a complete working solution for on-path user traffic telemetry in carrier networks.</t></abstract>

